	     MOVE 13		 TO SLIN.
	     MOVE 64		 TO SCOL.
	     ADD 1 SLIN 	 GIVING SHADE-ROW.
	     MOVE 18		 TO SHADE-COL.
	     MOVE 48		 TO SHADE-WIDTH.
	     MOVE 2		 TO SHADE-LINES.
	     DISPLAY ERROR-LINE AT LINE SLIN.
	     PERFORM SCREEN-SHADOW.
	     PERFORM HIDE-THE-CURSOR.
	     CALL X"AF" USING GET-SINGLE-CHAR, KEY-STATUS.
	     PERFORM DISPLAY-THE-CURSOR.
	     GO TO ROUTE-END-LOOKUP.

       ROUTE-ADJ-NO-KEYS.
           IF W75-S1 > 1
	       SUBTRACT 1	 FROM W75-S1 CLIN.
	     GO TO ROUTE-HIGHLIGHT.

       ROUTE-CHK-NO-KEYS.
	   IF W75-S1 = ZERO
	       MOVE 1		 TO W75-S1
	       GO TO ROUTE-HIGHLIGHT.
           IF W75-S1 < W75-S
	       ADD 1		 TO W75-S1 CLIN.

       ROUTE-HIGHLIGHT.
	     PERFORM ROUTE-CRT-ATTRIB.
	     DISPLAY W43-DET2A (CLIN) AT CPOS
		     WITH BACKGROUND-COLOR 5
			  FOREGROUND-COLOR 7.
	     GO TO ROUTE-GET-USER-OPT.

       ROUTE-CRT-EDGE.
012890	     DISPLAY
		  "³        ³                                        ³"
		   AT CPOS WITH BACKGROUND-COLOR 7
				FOREGROUND-COLOR 0
019260	     ADD 1		 TO CLIN.

       ROUTE-END-LOOKUP.
	   IF NOT (W75-S1 = ZERO)
	       MOVE W75-ROUTE (W75-S1)
				 TO W30-ROUTE.

       ROUTE-LOOKUP-EXIT.
             EXIT.
